## Query generation rules
- Use the exact column names as defined above (no renaming, no guessing).
- For filters by agency, derive `agency_id` through `public.users` and respect RLS.
- Prefer `SELECT ... FROM ... LEFT JOIN ... ON ...` with explicit conditions.
- If relationships or constraints are unclear, ask for clarification instead of guessing.
- For front-end layout suggestions, default to Flexbox for simple alignment tasks.

## Output rules
- When editing an existing file, show only the relevant diff/snippet.
- Keep comments short and practical.
- Follow the existing coding style in the project.